\v 46 and a buck of \sls (the)\sls* goats, for sin. \sls (and a goat buck, for a sin offering.)\sls*
\p 
\v 47 And into \sls (the)\sls* sacrifice of peaceable things \em he offered\em* two oxen, five rams, five goat bucks, five lambs of one year. This was the offering of Eliasaph, the son of Deuel. \sls (And for a peace offering, \em he offered\em* two oxen, five rams, five goat bucks, and five one-year-old lambs. This was the offering of Eliasaph, the son of Deuel.)\sls*
\p 
